    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. Rustle up this one pot twist on a takeaway fave. You'll simmer beef chuck, onions and peppers in an umami-packed black bean sauce before letting the oven work its magic. Dish up with baked rice and enjoy. Under 600 calories.",
